item.title: By: Machinato
item.dc:creator: Machinato
item.description: Oh how cool! I am most definitely going to buy this. I guess I had better begin following the Go Twitter community, huh? By the way, I never realized I could play a better game if I only pumped up my muscles and took my shirt off. I will need to try that Thursday night at the public library with my group. And maybe a sweatband.
